have agreed that Mr. O'Reilly
will not return

06:35.795 --> 06:37.663 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
to FOX News Channel."

06:37.697 --> 06:42.969 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
The popular TV host and
commentator has been
the face of the network for
nearly two decades.

06:43.002 --> 06:50.643 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That all began to unravel after
a New York
Times revealed that FOX paid
some $13 million

06:50.676 --> 06:56.549 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to settle allegations of sexual
harassment
filed by women O'Reilly worked
with.

06:56.582 --> 06:59.786 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Mr. O'Reilly has long denied
those allegations.

06:59.819 --> 07:04.657 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And in a statement late today,
he said: "It
is tremendously disheartening
that we part

07:04.690 --> 07:08.728 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
ways due to completely unfounded
claims.

07:08.761 --> 07:14.200 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But that is the unfortunate
reality many of
us in the public eye must live
with today."

07:14.233 --> 07:19.405 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
With these latest developments,
and what this
ouster may mean for a safer
workplace, I spoke

07:19.439 --> 07:23.543 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
