Schmidt, a reporter
with The New York Times team who
help break

07:23.576 --> 07:26.579 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the most recent story, and
Noreen Farrell.

07:26.612 --> 07:30.650 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
