civil rights
organization Equal Rights
Advocates.

07:30.683 --> 07:35.354 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I started by asking Schmidt what
changed the
minds of the Murdoch family.

07:35.388 --> 07:37.190 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
