today, where they
basically dismissed him.

08:36.249 --> 08:39.118 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: But it wasn't
just about money,
or was it?

08:39.151 --> 08:42.822 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
