sort of modernizing
it.

08:51.731 --> 08:55.902 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And what happened was is that
after Roger
Ailes left last summer, they
that said they

08:55.935 --> 09:00.006 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
were going to change the culture
and that
it was going to be different at
FOX and that

09:00.039 --> 09:03.276 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
