American values
and really preached them.

10:02.068 --> 10:07.607 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And that preachiness and his
tone, you know,
rubbed some people the wrong
way, but it also

10:07.640 --> 10:10.176 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
brought in some really, really
high ratings.

10:10.209 --> 10:14.113 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And he really established
himself and had
a real voice, more so than
anything.

10:14.146 --> 10:17.950 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And particularly to FOX, he was
seen as very
important because, at the 8:00
hour, he would

10:17.984 --> 10:21.754 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
