then 9:00 and
10:00 would have big ratings as
well.

10:21.787 --> 10:26.826 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, the question FOX, I think,
they were afraid
of is, well, if we take O'Reilly
out of 8:00,

10:26.859 --> 10:30.363 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
